title: Shocker Internet Drive In - Week 22: "Woof Woof" A Father's Day Special

sources.title: Shocker Internet Drive In - Week 22: "Woof Woof" A Father's Day Special
sources.description: Hello and Welcome Back! We may be a day or two late, but we are proud to bring our own special tribute to all the fathers out there. For today only, all you Dads out there get into the drive in for half price! And we have package of cinema sin set up just for you. After a few coming attractions and a rather fun dance number by Rachel Welch, we bring you that werewolf in presidential clothing, "Werewolf of Washington" followed by "The Rat Are Coming, The Werewolves Are Here" by Staten Island's version of Ed Wood - Andy Mulligan. So come on Dads and let the dogs out with our special "Woof Woof" double feature. NEW WEB ADDRESS: http://shockerdrivein.primehost24.tk
